{
  "stem": "1873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 381.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This way I started to work in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "To tell you what I have done in Sobibor, I must tell you the working of Sobibor, the mechanics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You see, I just finished my manuscript.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The title is But [INAUDIBLE], I put in three eventually titles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one, Of course, I do feel guilty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe the editor for Northwest University will consider this as a good title, because in a way, I feel guilty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What was-- I will explain-- what was the mechanics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I tell you the history of a Dutch transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A Dutch transport usually arrived in the morning, sometime in the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They arrived about two thousand people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "About 10 wagons were pushed in inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The rest waited outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The people were told to step down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Polish people were aware that it's a death camp, but the Dutch didn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They went down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was a group of us prisoners called bahnhof kommando.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We helped them with the heavy luggage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And us, you have seen in this film maybe, Some did even want to tip us for the help, for their heavy luggage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So unaware.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When they went down they were told to leave the heavy luggage and march on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The baggage will be delivered later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they marched on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They went to, to a big, huge barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "A German-- a barrack for German-- military barrack for German horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Was long with the entrance gate and the exit gate, the way you have it seen in the museum or maybe the model I made.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, why was this barrack built?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was built special, as I understood, for the woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because people departed with the valises.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the woman usually stick to the handbags.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have the most precious things there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
